{
  "stem": "1721.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A lot of them wanted to go back to Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A lot of them kept visiting Germany.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it wasn't until years later, I'm saying, what are you guys doing?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, they would never be able to make that separation.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they kept speaking German at home all the time.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They just never wanted to give that up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I guess those roots were so ingrained in them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they just-- they gave me no Judaism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Although my stepfather wasn't observant, but High Holy Days, he would go to temple.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My mother never went to temple at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I never had that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They attempted to send me to get a Jewish education in the Lower East Side when I was-- when we came over, but it was your archetypal Jewish scholar.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, the one that you see in the movie.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The little walk-up flat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The beard, and the yarmulke, and the dingy hall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It just wasn't-- I didn't mind that so much, but I didn't get this-- I didn't get this philosophical installation of being a Jew.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They just said, go there and learn.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So, it was very rote.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That didn't work very well.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So, finally, they dropped it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I didn't get encouragement at home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They didn't give me the value of being a Jew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They just said, go.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Because maybe the neighbors were doing it, too, and they just felt that I ought to do it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "So, but I knew I lived in a Jewish neighborhood.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And some of it came through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But then we would start wondering out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I started associating with other kids in the neighborhood, and we would wander outside the Jewish neighborhood towards the Italian neighborhood and Hell's Kitchen, and we would get into some altercations there, too.",
      "word_count": 33
    }
  ],
